			<div class="smallfont">Arch Mage</div>
			
					
			
				<div class="smallfont">
					&nbsp;<br /><a href="member.php?s=e10c32f9b81222ced0da9d7bbae5d802&amp;u=175"><img src="image.php?s=e10c32f9b81222ced0da9d7bbae5d802&amp;u=175&amp;dateline=1098531301" alt="Goladus's Avatar" border="0" /></a>
